1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:26,960
 When I pray in my office, which sits directly next to 635, I always do it with the awareness

2
00:00:26,960 --> 00:00:31,700
 in the background that traffic is just zooming by.

3
00:00:31,700 --> 00:00:35,880
 You can hear it, zoom, zoom, like everyone is racing to and fro.

4
00:00:35,880 --> 00:00:41,000
 They're trying to get wherever it is they're going.

5
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:49,040
 And it just stands as this great irony to me that in the middle of my moment of quiet,

6
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:52,360
 the world knows nothing about it.

7
00:00:52,360 --> 00:00:58,880
 But isn't there such clarity in the quiet, to have a moment to just reorient yourself,

8
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:05,000
 to kind of just stop everything as it was running and instead take a stand of faith.

9
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:08,560
 Because that's actually what you just did, whether you believe it or not.

10
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:15,840
 You just made a deliberate move away from the way in which everything normally runs.

11
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:20,100
 Like the rest of the world has already got you scheduled, your inbox is filling up as

12
00:01:20,100 --> 00:01:21,100
 we speak.

13
00:01:21,100 --> 00:01:24,160
 You haven't cleared them in the last week.

14
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:28,120
 Your calendar has things still set ahead.

15
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:35,140
 Your phones, which might've gone off in that moment, are trying to break into the silence

16
00:01:35,140 --> 00:01:36,920
 the world is wanting, man.

17
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:40,760
 They want for you to give them their attention.

18
00:01:40,760 --> 00:01:43,000
 And yet here's the amazing thing.

19
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:50,600
 What happens when we take our attention back?

20
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:53,240
 Something amazing happens.

21
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:56,060
 You make a declaration of faith.

22
00:01:56,060 --> 00:02:02,280
 You take a stand against the world, and you consecrate even just two minutes like we did,

23
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:06,240
