00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:36,200
 Have you ever had a moment like that?

47
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:41,160
 Where everything in you knows, like this isn't random, this isn't nothing.

48
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:42,160
