00:45:01,820 --> 00:45:04,180
 he find faith?"

704
00:45:04,180 --> 00:45:09,940
 Oh, God, let faith be found here.

705
00:45:09,940 --> 00:45:13,020
 Let faith rise up from within.

706
00:45:13,020 --> 00:45:22,940
 Let faith extend across our seats, into our city.

707
00:45:22,940 --> 00:45:25,740
 Let it extend, God, out over our country.

708
00:45:25,740 --> 00:45:33,260
 Let it make way into our office spaces, into our neighborhoods, across estranged relationships

709
00:45:33,260 --> 00:45:39,420
 in family lines, and then, God, let our faith rise up into heaven, and because, God, this

710
00:45:39,420 --> 00:45:47,420
 is our faith, a faith that says, "God, we believe you are who you say you are.

711
00:45:47,420 --> 00:45:54,980
 We believe you have done what you said you will do, and we believe you are coming again

712
00:45:54,980 --> 00:46:00,340
 as you have come before because we believe, oh, God.

713
00:46:00,340 --> 00:46:04,940
 Let mighty works be done here, and may you marvel at your people."

714
00:46:04,940 --> 00:46:05,940
 We love you.

715
00:46:05,940 --> 00:46:08,340
 It is in Christ's name we pray, amen.

